quran[7{c,v,t}:
11,82,phir jab hamaray faislay ka waqt aa pouncha to hum ne is bastii ko tall patt kar diya aur is par paki hui matti ke pathar tabrh toar barsaye
11,83,jin mein se har pathar tairay rab ke haan nishaan zada tha aur zaalmon se yeh saza kuch daur nahi hai
11,84,"aur Mudin walon ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai Shoiab ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo, is ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai aur naap toal mein kami nah kya karo aaj mein tum ko achay haal mein dekh raha hon, magar mujhe dar hai ke kal tum par aisa din aeye ga jis ka azaab sab ko ghair le ga"
11,85,"aur ae baradran qoum, theek theek insaaf ke sath poora ناپو aur tulo aur logon ko un ki cheezon mein ghata nah diya karo aur zameen mein fasaad nah pheilatay phiro"
11,86,"Allah ki di hui bachat tumahray liye behtar hai agar tum momin ho aur bahar haal mein tumahray oopar koi nigran car nahi hon """
11,87,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae Shoiab, kya teri namaz tujhe yeh sikhati hai ke hum un saaray mabodon ko chore den jin ki par- satish hamaray baap dada karte thay? ya yeh ke hum ko apne maal mein apne Mansha ke mutabiq tasarruf karne ka ikhtiyar nah ho? bas to hi to aik aliiiii zarf aurrasbaaz aadmi reh gaya hai! """
11,88,"Shoiab ne kaha"" bhayyo, tum khud hi socho ke agar mein apne rab ki taraf se aik khuli shahadat par tha aur phir is ne apne haan se mujh ko acha rizaq bhi ataa kya ( to is ke baad mein tumhari gmrahyon aur haraam khoryunmein tumhara shareek haal kaisay ho sakta hon? ) aur mein hargiz yeh nahi chahta ke jin baton se mein tum ko rokta hon un ka khud irtikaab karoon mein to islaah karna chahta hon jahan taq bhi mera bas chalay aur yeh jo kuch mein karna chahta hon is ka sara inhisaar Allah ki tofeq par hai, usi par mein ne bharosa kya aur har maamla mein isi ki taraf mein rujoo karta hon"
